snippet.title: Speed Maths for Fast Calculate Multiplication 2 - Sushi Monster
snippet.description:
Speed Maths for Fast Calculate Multiplication 2 - Sushi Monster.
Sushi Monster speed maths for fast calculate can you play game challenge with your friends and help you want faster math! A game to practice, reinforce, and extend math fact fluency is completely engaging and appropriately challenging with your friends. 

Features
• 12 CAREFULLY SEQUENCED LEVELS
• 7 addition levels
• 5 multiplication levels
• 4 rounds in each level
• 14 target numbers per round
• Replay each round with new numbers

Help to Subscribe this channel for more videos: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-CP3oXZjDiFGMqaxPxj_zw
Thanks for watching ^^
